akka.http.impl.engine.http2

Interface Http2StreamHandling


  • public interface Http2StreamHandling
    INTERNAL API

    Handles the 'incoming' side of HTTP/2 streams. Accepts FrameEvents from the network side and emits ByteHttp2SubStreams for streams to be handled by the Akka HTTP layer.

    Mixed into the Http2ServerDemux graph logic.
